<Heading Margin="Margin.Is3.FromBottom" Size="HeadingSize.Is1">Blazorise</Heading>

<Paragraph>
    Blazorise is a component library built on top of Blazor and CSS frameworks like <Anchor Target="Target.Blank" To="https://getbootstrap.com/">Bootstrap</Anchor>, <Anchor Target="Target.Blank" To="https://fluent2.microsoft.design/">FluentUI2</Anchor>, <Anchor Target="Target.Blank" To="https://tailwindcss.com/">Tailwind</Anchor>, <Anchor Target="Target.Blank" To="https://bulma.io/">Bulma</Anchor>, <Anchor Target="Target.Blank" To="https://ant.design/">Ant Design</Anchor>, and <Anchor Target="Target.Blank" To="http://daemonite.github.io/material/">Material</Anchor>. It can be used to build responsive, single-page web applications.
</Paragraph>

